  "title": "AB03 - Housekeeping Staff",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title : Housekeeper</strong></p><p>Location: Beach Rd</p><p>Working days :  6 days ; 8:30am -5:30pm </p><p>Salary : $ 2,000 -$2,400</p><p><strong>Responsibilities & Duties : </strong></p><ul><li>Cleans and makes up occupied rooms according to hotel standards by performing such daily activities as:</li><li>making beds, changing bedsheets and pillow cases</li><li>vacuuming the carpet</li><li>dusting and cleaning furniture</li><li>cleaning bathrooms and fixtures</li><li>changing towels and replenishing supplies such as soap, shampoo, stationery etc</li><li>cleaning drinking glasses</li><li>report defects in rooms</li><li>Perform any other duties assigned by Room Supervisor, Assistant Executive</li><li>Housekeeper or Executive Housekeeper.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>With relevant experience</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
